text: Nathania van Niekerk (born 22 January 1999) is a South African swimmer. She competed in the women's 200 metre backstroke at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships and she did not advance to the semi-finals. ==References== Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:South African female swimmers Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Swimmers at the 2014 Summer Youth Olympics Category:South African female backstroke swimmers
